In [[Europe]], Spanish is an official language of [[Spain]], the country after which it is named and from which it originated. It is also widely spoken in [[Gibraltar]] and [[Andorra]].<ref>{{cite web
|url=https://2009-2017.state.gov/r/pa/ei/bgn/3164.htm
